data.description: Here is a Bagley Special ready for a new owner. Take a look at this beautiful colonial style Home. You have four bedrooms ,1 and half bathrooms and a 2 Car garage. The kitchen has an open concept look and you have a great view of the dining room and living room. Going to the upstairs is where all the bedrooms are located and where the full bathroom is located as well. This property comes fully updated and comes with the stainless refrigerator, stove, Refrigerator seen in the photos.
